cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper focuses on deep learning methods for person detection in indoor environments, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of deep learning also suggests the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Additionally, the application of person detection in retail environments may also relate to multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
